					<p>Natural environments can be recognised by the following:<p>
					<ul><li>A variety of species growing in the same area</li>
						<li>Different layers in the vegetation that may include an understorey (such as grasses), a midstorey (such as smaller trees and shrubs), and an overstorey (the taller trees)</li></ul>
