        <div id="step_1" class="steps col-xs-6">
           <h1>Can you see the method of cultivation?</h1>
		   <p>
            <a target="_blank" id="uri" class="btn" href="http://blog.cafod.org.uk/tag/climate-change/"><i class="fa fa-white fa-search"></i>View context of this photo</a>
            </p>
			<div class="row help_popup col-xs-12">
			<i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i> How do I answer this question? <a class="help_popup_a" href="javascript:void(0)">Get some help</a>
				<div class="help_popup_description col-xs-12">
					<p>This helps us know what sort of machinery and/or tools are used in agricultural activities in an area. Machinery or tools could be damaged during a disaster and will need to be replaced before people can begin working their land again.</p>
					<p>Knowing the types of tools people are using can also give an idea of the agricultural production capabilities in an area. Those with with access to machinery and larger fields are likely to produce more than farmers working manually in smaller plots. At the same time, smaller subsistence farms might be more sensitive to drought and reduced yields are very likely to impact the local populations</p>
					<ul><li><strong>Manual cultivation:</strong> All the work is done by hand, or using hand-held, non mechanised tools such as scythes, hand-pushed plows etc. A person working in their fields with their hands would be an example of manual cultivation. However a person standing in the field does not indicate manual cultivation.</li>
						<li><strong>With animals:</strong> Similar to manual cultivation, however animals are used to help. If animals are involved they will often be hooked up to farming equipment</li>
						<li><strong>By machine:</strong> Machines are used to improve the efficiency of cultivation. Look for mechanised equipment and tools such as tractors</li>
					<hr>
					<p>Here are some examples of the different methods of cultivation:</p>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-sm-4">
							<p>Manual cultivation</p>
							<a target="_blank" href="http://slowpress.slowfood.it/upload/2012/658b727f54e64941504f0c317660dab7/img/risaia.jpg"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://slowpress.slowfood.it/upload/2012/658b727f54e64941504f0c317660dab7/img/risaia.jpg" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"><span class="fa fa-picture"></i> <a href="http://salonedelgustoterramadre.slowfood.com/dettaglioStampa.plp?tipo=UltimaOra&id=ffaeff4adcbb448264fb4a1bc28d1a3ben">International Salone del Gusto</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-4">
							<p>With animals</p>
							<a target="_blank" href="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Dhital-agri.JPG/1024px-Dhital-agri.JPG"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Dhital-agri.JPG/1024px-Dhital-agri.JPG" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"><span class="fa fa-picture"></i> <a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dhital-agri.JPG">Bishnu 35</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-4">
							<p>By machine</p>
							<a target="_blank" href="http://www.businessdailyafrica.com/image/view/-/1405796/medRes/141755/-/maxw/600/-/5djdw0/-/farmer.jpg"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://www.businessdailyafrica.com/image/view/-/1405796/medRes/141755/-/maxw/600/-/5djdw0/-/farmer.jpg" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"><span class="fa fa-picture"></i> <a href="http://www.businessdailyafrica.com/Mechanised-farming-holds-key-to-better-returns-from-agriculture-/-/1248928/1405790/-/e3l7un/-/index.html">Bishnu 35</a></p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<hr>
					<p>Here are some examples for which you should click "I don't know"</p>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-sm-4">
							<a target="_blank" href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_b5hcKABPlGI/TDA3E2lxhVI/AAAAAAAAg6Y/9A1caMvismw/s400/First+crop-1.jpg"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_b5hcKABPlGI/TDA3E2lxhVI/AAAAAAAAg6Y/9A1caMvismw/s400/First+crop-1.jpg" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"><span class="fa fa-picture"></i> <a href="http://newenergynews.blogspot.ch/2010/07/selfs-award-winning-solar-irrigation.html">S.E.L.F.</a></p>
