		 <!-- Step 4-->
        <div id="step_4" class="steps col-xs-6">
            <h1>Do the plants seem to be wilting? Or their leaves rolling?</h1>			
			<div class="row help_popup col-xs-12">
				<i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i>How do I answer this question? <a class="help_popup_a" href="javascript:void(0)">Get some help</a>
				<div class="help_popup_description col-xs-12">
					<p>Plants take water up from the soil. The water passes through the plant and evaporates via small pores called stomata on the leaves. This process is called transpiration. </p>
					<p>Rolling leaves in plants is a defence mechanism to minimise transpiration during times of water stress so the plant wonâ€™t lose too much water (<a href="http://vanishingbananas.blogspot.ch/2012/07/thirsty-corn-and-rolled-up-leaves.html">Click here for more info</a>). Therefore rolling leaves are a sign that there might be drought. </p>
					<p>Wilting of plants indicates that cells have begun to die and break down because of lack of water. Wilting plants might still be green but look limp, like they are falling over. They may even have begun to lose their green colour. The plant loses its green colour when the cell dies and the chlorophyll in the plant breaks down.</p>
					<hr>
					<p>Below are some examples of photos for which you would click "Yes":</p>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p>Rolling corn leaves caused by drought stress</p>
							<a href="http://www.agry.purdue.edu/ext/corn/news/articles.12/HotDryMidSeason-0625.html"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://www.agry.purdue.edu/ext/corn/news/articles.12/pix/20120624-002e.jpg" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"> <a href="http://www.agry.purdue.edu/ext/corn/news/articles.12/HotDryMidSeason-0625.html#">Purdue University</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p>Corn wilting and drying out due to drought stress</p>
							<a href="http://www.ianrpubs.unl.edu/pages/publicationD.jsp?publicationId=1048"><img style="width:400px;" src="http://www.ianrpubs.unl.edu/epublic/live/g1865/build/graphics/g1865-2.jpg" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
							<p style="font-size:10px;"> <a href="http://www.ianrpubs.unl.edu/pages/publicationD.jsp?publicationId=1048">University of Nebraska</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
