        <div id="step_5" class="steps col-xs-6">
            <h1>Does the crop appear to have been harvested?</h1>
			<div class="row help_popup col-xs-12">
				<i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i>How do I answer this question? <a class="help_popup_a" href="javascript:void(0)">Get some help</a>
				<div class="help_popup_description col-xs-12">
					<p>If the crop has been successfully harvested prior to or during the disaster then there was likely some food from it.</p>
					<p>Signs of harvest could be: <ul><li>Plants that are bent over or cut</li><li>Piles of plants that were cut down</li><li>Plants that look like the tops were cut off</li></ul></p>
					<hr>
					<p>Below are some examples of photos for which you would click "Yes"</p>
